  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Global Media Defence Fund</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The Global Media Defence Fund will specifically foster media protection and support the provision of legal advice to journalists, with a theory of change focused on the following aims:
&#x2022;	Foster international legal cooperation for promoting the defence of journalists under attack; 
&#x2022;	Reinforce the operationalization of national protection mechanisms and peer support networks;
&#x2022;	Support investigative journalism that contributes to reduced impunity for crimes against journalists;
&#x2022;	Enhance structures for fostering strategic litigation in order to protect a national environment where the legal frameworks are conducive to an independent, free and plural media ecosystem.</narrative>
  </description>
